   If your going after this one and if your around my lev or lower get some help on this one. You need to kill the spawn when they pop up in the throne room and the spawn at the throne area to get the templer.<BR>
  One more note: theres a lizzard that charms you and makes you attack your party so cautious on that. But note that my cha is low anyways. I was charmmed and end up killing my cleric and my enchanter. I Think its worth the risk.<BR>
